		descriptionLong : "These cute oversized pink and white oven mitts are made from the	strongest silk in the multiverse. While worn I'm unharmed by extreme temperatures outside 0\u00B0F and 100\u00B0F. If I'm hit by a ranged or thrown weapon attack, I can use a Reaction to reduce the damage by 1d10 plus my Dexterity modifier as long as I have a free hand. If I reduce the damage to zero, I can catch the ammunition or weapon if it's small enough to hold.",
		descriptionFull : "Cute oversized pair of pink and white oven mitts made from the strongest silk in the multiverse.\n   " + toUni("Temperate") + ". You are unharmed by temperatures of 0 degrees Fahrenheit or lower, and 100 degrees Fahrenheit or higher.\n   If you're hit by an attack roll made with a Ranged or Thrown weapon while wearing these gloves, you can take a Reaction to reduce the damage by 1d10 plus your Dexterity modifier if you have a free hand. If you reduce the damage to 0, you can catch the ammunition or weapon if it is small enough for you to hold in that hand.",
