		source : [["AL:SA","11A"]],
		rarity : "very rare",
		description : "Made of string, wood shavings, and dried mushrooms with a brass center, this tethered compass spins wildly in 60 ft of a planar portal. As a Magic action, I can name a familiar extraplanar location and make a DC 15 Int (Arcana) check. On success, I cast Plane Shift. On failure, me and each creature and object in 15 ft go to random location on another plane (d100). 1-60: Plane I named. 61-70: Inner Plane. 71-90: Outer Plane. 91-100 Astral Plane.",
		descriptionLong : "Made of string, wood shavings, & dried mushrooms with a brass center, this tethered compass spins wildly in 60 ft of a planar portal. As a Magic action, name a familiar extraplanar location & make a DC 15 Int (Arcana) check. On a success, I cast Plane Shift. On a failure, me & each creature or object in 15 ft travel to random location on another plane (d100). 1-60: Plane I named. 61-70: Inner Plane (1d6: 1/Air. 2/Earth. 3/Fire. 4/Water. 5/Feywild. 6/Shadowfell. 71-80: Outer Plane (1d8: 1/Arborea. 2/Arcadia. 3/Beastlands. 4/Bytopia. 5/Elysium. 6/Mechanus. 7/Mount Celestia. 8/Ysgard). 81-90: Outer Plane (1d8: 1/Abyss. 2/Acheron. 3/Carceri. 4/Gehenna. 5/Hades. 6/Limbo. 7/Nine Hells. 8/Pandemonium). 91-100 Astral Plane.",
		descriptionFull : "A tethered compass made of string, wood shavings, and dried mushrooms with a center of brass, this item spins wildly when within 60 feet of a gate or portal to another plane.\n   While wearing this amulet, you can take a magic action to name a location that you are familiar with on another plane of existence. Then make a DC 15 Intelligence (Arcana) check. On a successful check, you cast Plane Shift. On a failed check, you and each creature and object within 15 feet of you travel to a random destination by rolling 1d100 and consulting the following table.\n\n"+
		toUni("1d100\tDestination") + "\n01-60\tRandom location on the plane you named.\n61-70\tRandom location on an Inner Plane determined by rolling 1d6: on a 1, the Plane of Air; on a 2,\n\tthe Plane of Earth; on a 3, the Plane of Fire; on a 4, the Plane of Water; on a 5, the Feywild; on a 6,\n\tthe Shadowfell.\n71-80\tRandom location on an Outer Plane determined by rolling 1d8: on a 1, Arborea; on a 2, Arcadia; \n\ton a 3, the Beastlands; on a 4, Bytopia; on a 5, Elysium; on a 6, Mechanus; on a 7, Mount Celestia; \n\ton an 8, Ysgard.\n81-90\tRandom location on an Outer Plane determined by rolling 1d8: on a 1, the Abyss; on a 2, Acheron; \n\ton a 3, Carceri; on a 4, Gehenna; on a 5, Hades; on a 6, Limbo; on a 7, the Nine Hells; on an 8, \n\tPandemonium.\n91-00 \tRandom location on the Astral Plane",
