		description : "This red leather bag is 2 ft sq, 4 ft deep, & always weighs 5 lbs. It holds 500 lbs & 64 cu ft. Utilize to retrieve item. If overloaded, pierced, or torn, it' destroyed & contents go to the Astral plane. Turn inside out to empty bag. Has 10 min of air. One-way gate to Astral Plane opens if in similar extradimensional item space; all in 10 ft pulled in.",
