		descriptionLong: "This finely crafted tan bag is decorated with images of animals that randomly change each time I looked. It glows in the moonlight, shedding dim light in a 5-ft radius. When opened, I hear the sound of gently rustling leaves and a sonorous elven hymn. As Magic action 3 times per dawn, I can pull a fuzzy object from this bag and throw it 20 ft. It turns into a creature when it lands, determined randomly (d8): 1-jackal, 2-ape, 3-baboon, 4-axe beak, 5-black bear, 6-giant weasel, 7-giant hyena, 8-tiger. The creature is Friendly, acts on my turn, and vanishes at the next dawn or at 0 HP. As a bonus action, I can give it exact or general orders (e.g. attack my enemies). Without orders, it acts naturally.",
