		source : [["AL","WBW-DC"]],
		rarity : "very rare",
		description : "Gilded letters title this buoyant kelp book \"FAITHBRINGER: How to Stop Worrying & Start Worshiping.\" Smaller letters read: \"This book may change your life.\" It holds a list of sea gods & gives adv on Str (Athletics) chks to swim. When read, the seaweed makes a hoarse, \"Believe!\". If I study for 48 hrs over 6 days, my Cha score & max go up by 2 (max 30). The tome then loses its magic for 100 yrs.",
		descriptionLong : "This cover depicts a stormy sea, emblazoned with gilded letters titling it \"FAITHBRINGER: How to Stop Worrying and Start Worshiping.\" Smaller letters read: \"This book may change your life.\" The buoyant tome is inscribed on dried kelp, and features an exhaustive endorsement of every sea god in the Forgotten Realms. When perused, the crackles of the seaweed sound like a hoarse, \"Believe!\". The magic book contains tips for influencing and charming others. If I study it for 48 hrs in 6 days and practice its guidelines, my Charisma score and max increase by 2 (max 30). The tome then loses its magic for 100 years.",
		descriptionFull : "Emblazoned across the cover depicting a stormy sea, gilded letters pick out the title of FAITHBRINGER: How to Stop Worrying and Start Worshiping. In smaller letters it further reads, \"This book may change your life.\" The buoyant tome is inscribed on dried kelp, and features an exhaustive endorsement of every sea god throughout the Forgotten Realms. When perused, the leathery crackles of the seaweed sound like a hoarse, \"Believe!\"\n   " + toUni("Waterborne") + ". This item floats on water and other liquids. You have Advantage on Strength (Athletics) checks to swim.\n   " + toUni("Quirk: Loud") + ". The item makes a loud noisesuch as a clang, a shout, or a resonating gongwhen used. [GFP Item]\n   This book contains guidelines for influencing and charming others, and its words are charged with magic. If you spend 48 hours over a period of 6 days or fewer studying the book's contents and practicing its guidelines, your Charisma increases by 2, to a maximum of 30. The manual then loses its magic but regains it in a century.",
