		description : "This leathery cloak is made of the small green scales of a pteranodon and gives me a powerful appetite for fish. The cloak grants adv. on Stealth (Dex) checks. In dim light or darkness, I can use the cloak to fly while gripping the edges with both hands (40 ft Speed) and once per dawn turn into a bat with Polymorph, retaining my Int, Wis, and Cha.",
