		source : [["AL","FR-DC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This cloak was my prize when crowned Lunar Champion of the Many-Arrows' festival. It's embroidered with the insignia of the Many-Arrow (a skull pierced by three arrows) in beautiful red and gold thread, symbolizing good fortune, joy, and unity among the orc clans. When worn, I gain +1 to AC and saving throws. As a Magic action, it emits 10-ft bright light and 10-ft dim, or stops.",
