		source : [["AL","WBW-DC"]],
		rarity : "common",
		description : "This fine gown honors graduates of the Visitor Center's impressive school. It's a deep purple velvet with black satin trim and has a small ceremonial cape that falls down the back. I can speak Sylvan and use a bonus action to make the cape billow dramatically for 1 min.",
