		descriptionFull : "This chest of preserving has the beacon minor property only when the lid is open.\n   " + toUni("Beacon") + ". You can take a Bonus Action to cause the item to shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, or to extinguish the light.\n   Food and other perishable items do not age or decay while inside a Chest of Preserving. The chest is 2\xBD feet long, 1\xBD feet wide, and 1 foot tall with a half-barrel lid. The chest has a lock, which can be picked with thieves' tools and a successful DC 15 Dexterity check. Smashing the lock or any other part of the chest renders it nonmagical.",
