		description : "Food and other perishables don't age or decay inside this chest. It's 2.5 ft long, 1.5 ft wide, & 1 ft tall with a half-barrel lid. Its lock requires a DC 15 Dex (Thieves' Tools) check. Smashing the chest makes it nonmagical. As a bonus action, it sheds 10-ft bright light & 10-ft more dim, or stops. The chest's light also turns on when I open the lid for easy viewing. That light is contained within the chest.",
		descriptionLong : "While inside this chest, food and other perishables don't age or decay. It's 2.5 ft long, 1.5 ft wide, and 1 ft tall with a half-barrel lid. Its lock can be picked with a DC 15 Dex (Thieves' Tools) check. Smashing the lock or any part of the chest makes it nonmagical. It's light automatically turns on when the lid is opened to allow easy viewing. That light is contained within the chest. However, I can also use a bonus action to make it shed 10-ft bright light and 10-ft more dim, or stop.",
		descriptionFull : "The chest's light automatically turns on when the lid is opened to allow easy viewing of the contents. In this case, the light is contained within the chest.\n   " + toUni("Beacon") + ". You can take a Bonus Action to cause the item to shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, or to extinguish the light.\n   Food and other perishable items do not age or decay while inside a Chest of Preserving. The chest is 2\xBD feet long, 1\xBD feet wide, and 1 foot tall with a half-barrel lid. The chest has a lock, which can be picked with thieves' tools and a successful DC 15 Dexterity check. Smashing the lock or any other part of the chest renders it nonmagical.",
