		description : "Around this decanter are framed pictures of female humans and 'A Circle of Life Treats Everyone Alike'. As Magic action, open and say command, making fresh or salt water until my next turn. \"Splash\" for 1 gal. \"Fountain\" for 5 gal. \"Geyser\" for 30 gal in 30 ft \xD7 1 ft line. While held, aim line at 1 target. Creature makes DC 13 Str save or 1d4 Bludg. & Prone. If unattended obj up to 200 lbs, knocked over.",
