		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "Water from this flask glows softly in moonlight, casting 5 ft of dim light for a few moments. Imbibers hear mutters of long forgotten things, which is discomforting but can be useful. As Magic action, open it and say command, pouring out fresh/salt water until my next turn. \"Splash\" for 1 gal. \"Fountain\" for 5 gal. \"Geyser\" for 30 gal in 30 ft \xD7 1 ft line. I can aim line at 1 target. Creature makes DC 13 Str save or 1d4 Bludgeoning and Prone. If unattended obj up to 200 lbs, falls over.",
