		source : [["AL","DC-POA"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This green glass bottle is labeled \"Minerva's Mash\" and feels half full of liquid if shaken. I can open or close it as a Magic action. It emits smoke instead of spirits due to being exposed to fluctuating arcane energy. When open, heavily-obscuring smoke flows from the bottle in a 60-ft radius, increasing by 10 ft per min to 120 ft. Cloud disperses after 10 min or 1 min in strong wind.",
