		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This well-oiled quiver of blackened leather with small white stones sparkling like stars feels unusually light. When I take a long rest, I'm slightly uneasy if I can't see the sky. The quiver has 3 compartments and always weighs 2 lbs. The shortest holds 60 arrows, bolts, etc. The middle holds 18 javelins, etc. The longest holds 6 large objects, such as bows, quarterstaffs, or spears.",
