		descriptionFull : "This pen is tipped with an emerald nib and requires no ink to write. While holding this pen, you can cast illusory script at will, requiring no material components.\n   " + toUni("Waterborne") + ". This item floats on water and other liquids. You have advantage on Strength (Athletics) checks to swim.",
