		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "Woven by Flamsterd, this rope is made of soft kelp from the seafloor near his aquatic tower. It carries the faint scent of the sea. While held, magic action to entangle visible creature in 20 ft. Target makes DC 15 Dex save or Restrained. Let go or bonus action to free. Escape as action with DC 15 Dex (Acro)/Str (Athletics) chk. Reaction to coil in hand. The rope has AC 20, 20 HP, heals 1 HP per 5 min.",
