			source : [["AL","WBW-DC"]],
			rarity : "very rare",
			description : "This obsidian ki-rin figurine glows with golden scales. It lets me speak with horses & Infernal. As a Magic action, I can say command & throw to empty space in 60 ft. It becomes a Nightmare for 24 hrs, until I repeat action or it has 0 HP. It's Friendly, understands me, acts directly after me, & obeys my orders (10% to disobey each use). Fights only to defend self. See Notes.",
