		descriptionFull : "These slippers' are crafted of the finest supple deerskin, with iron studs crafted into the soles. Bright red, the color of pouring blood, they present a striking appearance. While you wear these boots, your steps make no sound, regardless of the surface you are moving across. You also have Advantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks.",
