		source : [["AL","S4"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "These light boots are made of supple, green leather & accented with dead leaves. They're constantly covered in muck as if I've been walking through ankle-deep, bloody gore. No amount of cleaning (magical or otherwise) removes the filth. While worn, my steps are silent, regardless of the surface. I have advantage on Dex (Stealth) checks.",
