	"boots of speed (wbw-dc-ucon-2)" : {
		name : "Boots of Speed (WBW-DC-UCON-2)",
		source : [["AL","WBW-DC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		attunement : true,
		description : "These boots are very soft and have a curled toe in their natural form. They're imbued with illusion magic, letting me alter their appearance in minor ways. Such changes don't affect their properties. As a bonus action, I can click heels to double my Speed and give Opportunity Atks against me disadv. Repeat bonus action to end. The boots can be used for 10 min per long rest.",
		descriptionFull : "These boots are very soft and in their natural form they have a curled toe at the end.\n   " + toUni("Illusion") + ". The item is imbued with illusion magic, allowing its bearer to alter the item's appearance in minor ways. Such alterations don't change how the item is worn, carried, or wielded, and they have no effect on its other magical properties. For example, the wearer could make a red robe appear blue, or make a gold ring look like it's made of ivory. The item reverts to its true appearance when no one is carrying or wearing it.\n   While you wear these boots, you can take a Bonus Action to click the boots' heels together. If you do, the boots double your Speed, and any creature that makes an Opportunity Attack against you has Disadvantage on the attack roll. If you click your heels together again, you end the effect.\n   When you've used the boots' property for a total of 10 minutes, the magic ceases to function for you until you finish a Long Rest.",
		action : [["bonus action", "Boots of Speed (start/stop)"]],
		limfeaname : "Boots of Speed",
		usages : 10,
		recovery : "long rest",
		additional : "minutes",
	},
