		rarity : "uncommon",
		attunement : true,
		description : "These tall leather boots are wrapped in fur and tied with brightly dyed rawhide. They expand or contract to fit me snugly, giving me a sense of sure-footedness in snow or icy terrain. My Speed is 30 ft unless higher and isn't reduced by encumbrance or heavy armor. Once per turn, I can jump up to 30 ft with only 10 ft of movement.",
		descriptionFull : "These tall, leather boots are wrapped in fur tied on with brightly dyed rawhide. It expands or contracts to fit the wearer snugly, giving the wearer a sense of sure-footedness in snowy or icy terrain (there is no mechanical benefit to this).\n   While you wear these boots, your Speed becomes 30 feet unless your Speed is higher, and your Speed isn't reduced by you carrying weight in excess of your carrying capacity or wearing Heavy Armor.\n   Once on each of your turns, you can jump up to 30 feet by spending only 10 feet of movement.",
