		descriptionFull : "These boots are navy blue, featuring black feathers adorning the sidewall, and white embroidery in a feather pattern adorning the toe. In addition, these boots let you take a Magic action to cause your voice or signal to carry clearly for up to 600 feet until the end of your next turn. The wearer's voice takes on a distinctly bird-like squawking quality when using this minor property.\n   These boots have 4 charges and regain 1d4 expended charges daily at dawn. While wearing the boots, you can take a Magic action to expend 1 charge, gaining a Fly Speed of 30 feet for 1 hour. If you are flying when the duration expires, you descend at a rate of 30 feet per round until you land.",
