		name : "Winged Boots (FR-DC-DOG)",
		source : [["AL","FR-DC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "Twig Medo got these boots from his pa but never wore them due to a fear of witchcraft and dark magic. They have 4 charges, 1d4 regained at dawn. I can use 1 charge as a Magic action to gain a 30 ft Fly Speed for 1 hr. If flying when the time expires, I descend 30 ft per round. While worn, I'm unharmed by extreme temps past 0\u00B0F and 100\u00B0F.",
		descriptionFull : "\"me pa gave me these wikked boots, sed let me fay. naver dared uear emtoo skeered of uitchkraf. u seen wut hieppen to Glib when em messed with dark magik. - Twig Medo\"\n   " + toUni("Temperate") + ". You are unharmed by temperatures of 0 degrees Fahrenheit or lower, and 100 degrees Fahrenheit or higher.\n   These boots have 4 charges and regain 1d4 expended charges daily at dawn. While wearing the boots, you can take a Magic action to expend 1 charge, gaining a Fly Speed of 30 feet for 1 hour. If you are flying when the duration expires, you descend at a rate of 30 feet per round until you land.",
