		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This conical party hat is wrapped in rainbow ribbons. While wearing it, I can cast Disguise Self. The spell ends if the hat is removed.",
		descriptionFull : "This hat is shaped like a conical party hat, wrapped in rainbow-colored ribbons.\n   While wearing this hat, you can cast the Disguise Self spell. The spell ends if the hat is removed.",
