		description : "This stylish beret is bright pink with a glorious black feather. Sewn on the inside is a printed inscription proclaiming it \"Property of the Thentian Library of Arcane History\". I can cast Comprehend Languages from it unless I've raised my voice above a courteous whisper in a library. Then the beret ceases to function for 10 minutes. (Helm of Comprehending Languages)",
		descriptionLong : "This wonderfully stylish beret is bright pink and adorned with a glorious black feather. Carefully sewn on the inside is a neatly printed inscription proudly proclaiming it \"Property of the Thentian Library of Arcane History\". While worn, I can cast Comprehend Languages from it unless I've raised my voice above a courteous whisper in a library. Then the beret ceases to function for 10 minutes. (Helm of Comprehending Languages)",
		descriptionFull : "This wonderfully stylish beret is bright pink and adorned with a glorious black feather. Carefully sewn on the inside is a neatly printed inscription proudly proclaiming it as \"Property of the Thentian Library of Arcane History\". When worn, the beret functions exactly as a Helm of Comprehending Languages, except in the event that the wearer is located in a library and has raised their voice level above a courteous whisper. In this case, the beret ceases to function for 10 minutes.\n   While wearing this helm, you can cast Comprehend Languages from it.",
