		descriptionLong : "This helm looks like a black-visored barbuta crafted from black iron. It's warm to the touch with sigils of flames covering the surface in shades of red and orange. The helm once belonged to a powerful eldritch knight who was killed in battle with unspeakable evil. It features in a prophecy and whispers to me to become more powerful for the evil might return. While worn, I can cast Comprehend Languages from it.",
		descriptionFull : "The item is warm to the touch, and any metal parts are crafted from black iron. Sigils of flames cover its surface. Shades of red & orange are the prominent colors. The item also features in a prophecy.\n   This helm once belonged to a powerful eldritch knight who rivaled the most powerful archmages of his time. It looks like a black visored barbuta. He was killed in a battle with an unspeakable evil. The helm whispers to its bearer to become more powerful for it might return.\n   While wearing this helm, you can cast Comprehend Languages from it.",
