		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This pink shimmery jellyfish was beautifully preserved by Jilly Stillwater & is perfectly odorless. The long tendrils serve as a scarf when used as a hat. I can cast Comprehend Languages from it & use imbued illusion magic to alter its appearance in minor ways.",
		descriptionFull : "A pink jellyfish has been beautifully preserved by Jilly Stillwater such that it remains perfectly odorless. The long tendrils also serve as a scarf whenever the shimmery jellyfish is used as a hat.\n   " + toUni("Illusion") + ". The item is imbued with illusion magic, allowing its bearer to alter the item's appearance in minor ways. Such alterations don't change how the item is worn, carried, or wielded, and they have no effect on its other magical properties. For example, the wearer could make a red robe appear blue, or make a gold ring look like it's made of ivory. The item reverts to its true appearance when no one is carrying or wearing it.\n   While wearing this helm, you can cast Comprehend Languages from it.",
