		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "uncommon",
		description : "This helm uses just enough material to protect vital areas, leaving cosmetic gaps and slits. The distinct geometric design stands out, but also allows it to be hidden easily under a cloak. While worn, I have 30 feet of Telepathy. I can also cast Detect Thoughts and Suggestion (save DC 13) once per dawn each.",
