		source : [["AL","SJ-DC"]],
		rarity : "common",
		description : "Bookworm, an aspiring inventor, tried to make a loud horn for their next driving lesson, but accidentally crafted this instead. The horn has 4 charges, regaining 1d4 at dawn. As Magic action, use 1 charge & blow it: 1 chosen creature in 600 ft hears the horn unless it's Deafened. Inspired by my defense of the Tavern at the End of the Wildspace, the horn warns me, giving +2 initiative if not Incapacitated.",
