		description : "As a Magic action once per 7 days, I can blow this iron horn to summon 5 warrior spirits (Berserkers) in 60 ft. They are immune to Charmed and Frightened and disappear after 1 hr or at 0 HP. If I'm proficient with martial weapons, they're Friendly and obey me. If not, they attack. The horn also warns me, giving +2 initiative unless Incapacitated.",
