		name : "Horn Appetit! (Iron Horn of Valhalla, IC)",
		source : [["AL","PS-DC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "This shining dwarven iron horn is cool to touch. The engraved sides show great dwarven feasts, huge kegs of ale, & the slaying of monstrous beasts like tarrasques & krakens. It's bearer can speak Common. As Magic action once per 7 days, summon 5 monster cuisine cooks from Butcher's Bounty in 60 ft, with uniforms & giant cleavers. The Berserkers are immune to Charmed & Frightened & disappear after 1 hr or at 0 HP. If proficient with martial weapons, they're Friendly & obey me. If not, they attack.",
		descriptionLong : "The shining iron horn is dwarven and cool to the touch. Elegantly engraved into the sides are scenes of great dwarven feasts, huge kegs of ale, and the slaying of monstrous beasts such as a tarrasque and a kraken. Anyone holding the horn can speak Common. As a Magic action once per 7 days, I can blow the horn to summon 5 warrior spirits (Berserkers) in 60 ft. They look like monster cuisine cooks from the Butcher's Bounty, wearing their uniforms and wielding giant cleavers. The cooks are immune to Charmed and Frightened and disappear after 1 hr or at 0 HP. If I'm proficient with martial weapons, they're Friendly and obey me. If not, they attack.",
		descriptionFull : "The shining iron horn is of dwarven make and cool to the touch. Elegantly engraved into the sides of the horn are scenes of great dwarven feasts, huge kegs of ale, and the slaying of monstrous beasts which include a tarrasque and a kraken. When the horn is blown, it summons monstercuisine cooks from the Butcher's Bounty, wearing their uniforms and wielding giant cleavers.\n   " + toUni("Language") + ". The bearer can speak and understand Common.\n    You can use a Magic action to blow this horn. In response, warrior spirits from the plane of Ysgard appear within 60 feet of you. These spirits use the Berserker statistics. They return to Ysgard after 1 hour or when they drop to 0 hit points. Once you use the horn, it can't be used again until 7 days have passed.\n   The iron horn summons 5 berserkers. To use the iron horn, you must be Proficient with all Martial Weapons.\n   If you blow the horn without meeting its requirement, the summoned Berserkers attack you. If you meet the requirement, they are friendly to you and your companions and follow your commands.",
