		descriptionFull : "This horn is covered in images of small horses eating spaghetti. When it is blown, the berserkers that come forth are in fact, Waffles (horse people) from the Domain of Dreams' Hoard. It gives a slightly warm glow when it is near dragons.\n   " + toUni("Sentinel") + ". This item glows faintly when a creatures of the dragon type are within 120 feet of it.\n    You can take a Magic action to blow this horn. In response, warrior spirits from the plane of Ysgard appear in unoccupied spaces within 60 feet of you. Each spirit uses the Berserker stat block and returns to Ysgard after 1 hour or when it drops to 0 Hit Points. The spirits look like living breathing warriors, and they have Immunity to the Charmed and Frightened conditions. Once you use the horn, it can't be used again until 7 days have passed.\n    The silver horn summons 2 Berserkers. They are Friendly to you and your allies and follow your commands.",
