		source : [["AL","WBW-DC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "This magical Ophicleide from the age of enlightenment can bring dream warriors into reality. As a bonus action, it sheds 10-ft bright light & 10-ft more dim, or stops. With a Magic action once per 7 days, I can blow the horn to summon 2 warrior spirits in 60 ft. These Berserkers can't be Charmed or Frightened, disappear after 1 hour or at 0 HP, are Friendly & obey my orders.",
		descriptionLong : "A magical Ophicleide from the age of enlightenment that can bring warriors of dreams into reality. As a bonus action, it sheds bright light in a 10-ft radius and 10-ft more dim light, or stops. Using a Magic action once per 7 days, I can blow the horn to summon 2 warrior spirits within 60 ft. These Berserkers are immune to Charmed and Frightened, disappear after 1 hour or at 0 HP, are Friendly and obey my commands.",
		descriptionFull : "A magical Ophicleide from the age of enlightenment. Its sound is capable of bringing warriors of dream into reality.\n   " + toUni("Beacon") + ". You can take a Bonus Action to cause the item to shed Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet, or to extinguish the light.\n    You can take a Magic action to blow this horn. In response, warrior spirits from the plane of Ysgard appear in unoccupied spaces within 60 feet of you. Each spirit uses the Berserker stat block and returns to Ysgard after 1 hour or when it drops to 0 Hit Points. The spirits look like living breathing warriors, and they have Immunity to the Charmed and Frightened conditions. Once you use the horn, it can't be used again until 7 days have passed.\n    The silver horn summons 2 Berserkers. They are Friendly to you and your allies and follow your commands.",
