		descriptionFull : "This amulet is crafted from the tooth of a green dragon named Azdraka, who once terrorized the High Road south of Neverwinter and was slain by Lady Tanamere Alagondar.\n   " + toUni("Language") + ". The bearer can speak and understand draconic while the item is on the bearer's person.\n   This delicate silver chain has a brilliant-cut black gem pendant. While you wear it, you have Immunity to the Poisoned condition and Poison damage.",
