		description : "This dark-purple necklace bears the symbol of Mystryl. It wards off all poisons and glows when Undead are within 120 ft. While worn, I'm immune to the Poisoned condition and Poison damage.",
		descriptionFull : "This dark-purple necklace bears the symbol of Mystryl. Its final bits of power wards off all poisons and glows when it detects undead creatures.\n   " + toUni("Sentinel") + ". This item glows faintly when undead are within 120 feet of it.\n   This delicate silver chain has a brilliant-cut black gem pendant. While you wear it, you have Immunity to the Poisoned condition and Poison damage.",
