		description : "A beautiful necklace with a cerulean gem, given to me by King Neravas for liberating his kingdom from Silkarras influence. While worn, I'm immune to being Poisoned and Poison dmg. The necklace floats on liquids and gives adv on Str (Athletics) checks to swim.",
