		description : "This transparent glass sphere contains a minotaur's eyeball suspended in formaldehyde & acts as an arcane focus. As a Magic action while held, the eye points to magnetic north, if it exists. Otherwise, the eye looks at me, but quickly rotates away if I glance at it. While underground, I can make the eye look toward the nearest staircase, ramp, or other upward path.",
