		descriptionFull : "This ring has the Illusion minor property. In its normal state, it is made of bone, with flakes of obsidian creating tiny feathered wings to either side of a central trilliant cut ruby.\n   " + toUni("Illusion") + ". The item is imbued with illusion magic, allowing its bearer to alter the item's appearance in minor ways. Such alterations don't change how the item is worn, carried, or wielded, and they have no effect on its other magical properties. For example, the wearer could make a red robe appear blue, or make a gold ring look like it's made of ivory. The item reverts to its true appearance when no one is carrying or wearing it.\n   When you fall while wearing this ring, you descend 60 feet per round and take no damage from falling.",
