		source : [["AL","CCC"]],
		rarity : "rare",
		description : "The weathered silver ring is shaped like a flying gull with its wings creating the ring. Tiny runes on the inside write the word \"wind\" in Netherese. I feel energetic and curious, always looking for adventure and challenge. Difficult terrain doesn't cost me extra movement and magic can't reduce my Speed nor make me Paralyzed or Restrained.",
		descriptionFull : "The ring is a weathered silver ring of a flying gull with its wings becoming the ring. Tiny runes can be seen on the inside describing the word wind' in Netherese. The wearer of the ring feels energetic and curious, always looking for adventure and challenge.\n   While you wear this ring, Difficult Terrain doesn't cost you extra movement. In addition, magic can neither reduce any of your Speeds nor cause you to have the Paralyzed or Restrained condition.",
