		type : "rod",
		rarity : "very rare",
		description : "This sceptor is shaped like a broadsword with a pitted edge. Dwarvish runes on one side of the blade spell out its name, Bulwark. I can attune to the scepter in 1 min and use it as an arcane focus. I also gain resistance to Fire and Lightning damage and as an action, can use it to cast Thunderwave as a 4th-level spell (save DC 16) at will.",
