		description : "This rod is steel grey with unknown geometric runes and feels strangely cool. Each end features a 100-sided shape. In the center, a rectangular button rises up 1/4-in. When used, my voice deepens by 1 octave for 1d4 hrs. After 3 uses, this is permanent. Utilize action to push the button, magically securing or releasing it. Once fixed, it holds 8000 lbs; falls if more. Utilize DC 30 Str check to move 10 ft.",
