		source : [["AL","SJ-DC"]],
		description : "This pole smells faintly of hamsters and elderberries and can only be broken by special means. While held, I can use a Magic action to shrink it into a 1-ft rod. Its weight doesn't change. Repeat action to revert it to a Pole, up to 10-ft if space allows.",
