		description : "This large trophy, carved from magically treated amethyst, proclaims me the winner of Paup Quizzem's Greatest Gameshow and gives adv on Str saves. It has 6 charges, 1d6 regained at dawn. As a bonus action, 1 charge for Fly Speed equal to my Speed for 10 min and hover. As an action, 1 charge to have visible creature in 60 ft make a DC 18 Str save or be pushed 20 ft in any direction. I can also use 3 charges to cast Reverse Gravity (DC 18). Bonus action for 10-ft bright light and 10-ft dim, or stop.",
