		descriptionLong : "This 12\xD76\xD76 inch wooden box floats and can store items. As a Magic action, I can speak one of three command words. The first makes the box unfold into a Rowboat (AC 11, HP 50, Speed 1 mph, Crew 1, Passengers 3). The second causes it to unfold into a Keelboat (AC 15, HP 100, Speed 1 mph, Dmg Threshold 10, Crew 1, Passengers 6, Cargo 1/2 ton). When unfolded, the name \"Lavinia\" is painted in flowing script on the stern in honor of Yul Khahan's grandmother. The third command causes it to fold up if no one is aboard; any objects that don't fit in the box remain outside. Folded or unfolded, it's covered in delicate Gur pattern-work. If either vessel reduced to 0 HP, item is destroyed.",
