		rarity : "rare",
		description : "When all 4 of these horseshoes are affixed to the hooves of a horse or similar creature (Magic action for each), its Speed increases by 30 ft. While active, they flicker like flames from a torch and shed light in a 20-ft radius.",
		descriptionFull : "While active, these horseshoes flicker as if flames from a torch and shed light in a 20-foot radius.\n   These horseshoes come in a set of four. As a Magic action, you can touch one of the horseshoes to the hoof a horse or similar creature, whereupon the horseshoe affixes itself to the hoof. Removing a horseshoe also takes a Magic action.\n   While all four horseshoes are attached to the same creature, its Speed is increased by 30 feet."
